{"tid":2240241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★長沙灣藥房涉售有毒\"支製\"甲醇消毒酒精 一名48歲男董事被捕","createTime":"2020-10-12T13:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T14:12:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"375784ea26d427888996420048ff98ed485900cb","tid":2240241,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1554307_1_20201012210638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1554307_1_20201012210638.jpg&h=6e67dc27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關搜查長沙灣一間藥房，檢獲3樽含有毒甲醇成分的消毒酒精，化驗顯示，消毒酒精含有高達90%的甲醇，乙醇含量則只有少於2.7%，遠低於標示聲稱含有95%乙醇，與產品說明不符，藥房一名48歲男董事被捕。<br />\n<br />\n根據海關提供的圖片，該款含毒甲醇的酒精，由<span class=\"xx-large\">廣東佛山市「壹純有限公司」生產，</span>標示說明為簡體字，聲稱可用於皮膚表面消毒殺菌。<br />\n<br />\n海關說，根據化驗結果，涉案消毒酒精的乙醇含量與產品說明不符，而且含有毒甲醇成分，涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》及《消費品安全條例》。<br />\n<br />\n海關早前在這間藥房試購這款以透明膠樽銷售的消毒酒精，零售價每樽90元。海關呼籲市民馬上停用該款消毒酒精，商戶如有出售，亦應立即下架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554307-20201012.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554307-20201012.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=c6dda97a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554307-20201012.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8cea0764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554307-20201012.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c43c25fdc4a127fe38fbba4dce846aaeea0c34dc","tid":2240241,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji